data.description: ***JAW DROPPING OUTDOOR LIVING SPACE***Don't miss this modern farmhouse in one of Edmond's newest developments! This well-appointed home is situated on a large corner lot and is exploding with character, natural light, and space! The moment you walk in your eyes are drawn to the massive sliding glass wall that leads to the outdoor living space of your dreams complete with fireplace and grill. From the luxurious master suite to the large bonus room, to the stone fireplace, this home has it all! Not only will you fall in love with this home, the neighborhood is one of a kind as well! It will only feature historical architecture--farmhouse, bungalow, Tudor, and craftsman. This combined with the gated entry, fruit tree orchard, and community pavilion means this will soon be one of Edmond's most sought after developments. In order to find the house, please put the following address into GPS: 12550 S Broadway. This will take you to the entrance of the neighborhood.
